Teltoli / Kit
-------

Teltoli yawns again and rubs her eyes with a paw. She didn't know she was so tired, it must have been the strains of battle. Her eyelids drooped, but they snapped open again. 

"Oh great.. I know.. I'm.. not.. going to be.. able.. to.." She starts to say before falling asleep in the hallway in beast mode, her head resting between her paws.

--------

Kit wakes up and stretches, smiling at the day. Aaahh.. it felt good to be alive on such a day as this, she thought with a small smile. Now to find some fun..

She headed out, singing loudly with a better voice than one would have thought she had.
